{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.findSpecs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorems</span>.<span class=\"name\">findSpecs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">database</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Meta.Sym.SymM</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Except\">Except</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Look up `SpecTheorem`s in the `@[spec]` database.\nTakes all specs that match the given program `e` and sorts by descending priority.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.findSpecs","kind":"def","line":126,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.findSpecs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L126-L155"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.extendWithSimpSpecs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">extendWithSimpSpecs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">database</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecAttr.SpecTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">simpThms</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorems\">Meta.SimpTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecAttr.SpecTheorems</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Extend the `@[spec]` database with the equational lemmas registered through the `mvcgen_simp`\nside of `@[spec]`:\n- simp theorem declarations registered directly as `@[spec]`,\n- unfold entries registered with `attribute [spec] foo`, using stored equation lemmas when\n  available and falling back to `Meta.getEqnsFor?`.\n\nHoare triple and `⊑ wp` specs are already in `database`: the attribute stores them pattern-keyed\nat annotation time.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.extendWithSimpSpecs","kind":"def","line":81,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.extendWithSimpSpecs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L81-L122"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.global?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorem</span>.<span class=\"name\">global?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">specThm</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The declaration name of a global spec theorem, `none` for local/syntactic specs. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.global?","kind":"def","line":75,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.global?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L75-L77"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.instantiate\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorem</span>.<span class=\"name\">instantiate</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">specThm</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> (<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.BinderInfo\">BinderInfo</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Instantiates a spec theorem's proof.\n\nHoare triple and `⊑ wp` specs are normalised to `pre ⊑ wp …` form via `tripleToWpProof?`.\nSimp specs keep the raw `lhs = rhs` equality, but eta-expand function-level equations:\nfor unfold equations of class projections (e.g., `MonadState.modifyGet.eq_1`), the equation\nafter `forallMetaTelescope` may be between functions rather than values:\n  `@modifyGet σ m self = self.3 : {α} → (σ → α × σ) → m α`\nThis method applies `congrFun` for each leading forall to reduce the equation to one between\nvalues of type `m α`, introducing fresh metavariables for the extra arguments.\nThe number of extra args is stored in `SpecTheoremKind.simp etaArgs`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.instantiate","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem.instantiate","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L47-L73"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern.shareCommon\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Pattern</span>.<span class=\"name\">shareCommon</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Pattern.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern\">Pattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Pattern.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern\">Pattern</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Internalizes the pattern's expressions into the current `SymM` share table.\n\nA pattern is built in `MetaM`, outside the `SymM` thread whose table the targets are internalized\ninto, so its closed subterms (the instance telescope of a `wp` application, for example) are\nstructurally equal to but distinct from the targets'. Internalizing the pattern once makes those\nsubterms pointer-equal to every target internalized afterwards, so matching them is `O(1)`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern.shareCommon","kind":"def","line":34,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern.shareCommon","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L34-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isShared\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">isShared</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if `e` is already internalized into the current `SymM` share table, in which case\n`shareCommon e` returns `e` unchanged. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isShared","kind":"def","line":29,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.isShared","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.lean#L29-L32"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Attr","Lean.Meta.DiscrTree.Util","Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DiscrTree","Lean.Meta.Sym.Util"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SpecDB"}